description:
Vendetta is Vendetta, Ranked Number ONE for a reason, nothing else to say.
Naudia Nyce has a boxing trainer and is an very good amateur boxer, she is in shape and is the type of girl that when she goes out she usually gets in a fight, boys, girls it doesn't matter. Naudia will throw down on anyone. However boxing isn't wrestling and US wrestlers are not intimidated easily.
title: Vendetta(10-3) Ranked 1st
